    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "最终确认：六个博弈节点横向排列，Code→Define←Audit，Define→Barg↔Bail，Risk→Signal→Barg，外加独立的Place→Press。结构完整。",
